Main Street, west side, south from 59th Avenue (foreground), showing the area where new housing developments will be erected. The dwellings under construction in the center background are on Horace Harding Boulevard, Main Street being on the extreme left and is a new thoroughfare here.

P. L. Sperr

April 19, 1936
Views 1,2
